# build outputs (libfluke.a/.so + objects live here)
lib/
*.d

# python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
pyvenv/
.venv/

# AOT-exported fused-kernel artifacts are build outputs, NOT committed. Regenerate per arch
# before `make cuda=1` / `make rocm=1`:
#   CUDA (sm80):     cute/**/export_*.py           -> artifacts/sm80/*.{h,o}
#   RDNA4 (gfx12xx): fly/rdna4/**/export_*.py      -> artifacts/<gfxNNNN>/*.{h,hsaco}
# They are bundled into libfluke.a at build time (objcopy-embedded for HIP; symbol-rewritten
# .o for CUDA). The Makefile fails with a clear message if an expected artifact is missing.
artifacts/
